msgid: Overwrite the selected preset with the currently selected nodes.
zh_HANS: 用当前选中的节点覆盖选定的预设.

msgid: Extend the node add menu (Shift + A menu) to access and add your custom nodes.
zh_HANS: 扩展节点添加菜单 (Shift + A 菜单) 以访问和添加自定义节点.

msgid: Enable development mode for Hot Node (Wont having any effect in the release version).
zh_HANS: 启用 Hot Node 开发者模式 (在正式版本中不会有任何效果).

msgid: Root directory to store Hot Node data
zh_HANS: 存储Hot Node数据的根目录

msgid: Directory to match and load images from when getting nodes from preset.
zh_HANS: 从预设获取节点时匹配和加载图像的目录.

msgid: Items to show in the add-on panel
zh_HANS: 在插件面板中显示的项目
合并的保存节点菜单标签. 提示: "Save Nodes" 将被自动翻译.

msgid: Name of the extended menu for saving custom nodes.
zh_HANS: 保存自定义节点的扩展菜单名称.

msgid: Create a new preset with selected nodes.
zh_HANS: 用选定的节点创建新预设.

msgid: Refresh and load all packs and presets.
zh_HANS: 刷新并加载所有节点包和预设.

msgid: The preset tree type does not match the current node tree type.
zh_HANS: 预设树类型与当前节点树类型不匹配.

msgid: Extend the context menu (Right-click menu) to save custom nodes.
zh_HANS: 扩展上下文菜单 (右键菜单) 以保存自定义节点.
将预设移动到另一个节点包.

msgid: Overwrite existing files if they exist. If not checked, the re-named pack will get an unique name.
zh_HANS: 如果文件存在则覆盖现有文件, 如果关闭则重命名的节点包将获得唯一名称.

msgid: The preset file does not exist. Hot Node refreshed.
zh_HANS: 预设文件不存在. Hot Node 已刷新.

msgid: Get nodes from preset and add to the node tree.
zh_HANS: 从预设获取节点并添加到节点树.
历史数据不匹配. 已清空历史记录.

msgid: Pack name for creation, will be used when creating a new preset
Load and update all packs saved with previous versions of Hot Node.
zh_HANS: 加载并更新旧版 Hot Node 遗留的节点包.

msgid: Preset name for creation, will be used when creating a new preset
Move the selected preset up or down in the list.
zh_HANS: 在列表中上下移动选定的预设.

msgid: Decide what to do when a node tree with the same name already exists.
zh_HANS: 决定当同名节点树已存在时的处理方式.

msgid: (Will significantly increase file size and slow down the add-on) Maximize compatibility for presets to work fine with future versions of Blender.
zh_HANS: (将显著增加文件大小和拖慢运行速度) 最大化预设兼容性以确保其能在未来版本的 Blender 中正常工作.

msgid: Only match images having this key
zh_HANS: 仅匹配具有此关键字的图像

msgid: No node data found in the preset.
zh_HANS: 在预设中未找到节点数据.

msgid: Import preset pack(s) from zip file.
Minimum length of the list to show in UI
zh_HANS: 在 UI 中显示列表的最小长度

msgid: Filter for image names when loading images.
zh_HANS: 加载图像时的图像名称过滤器.

msgid: Delete selected preset from the pack.
zh_HANS: 从节点包中删除选定的预设.

msgid: Number of undo steps to keep

zh_HANS: 最小 UI 列表长度

msgid: No legacy packs found to update.
zh_HANS: 未找到要更新的旧版节点包.

msgid: Addon panel category to show in the UI sidebar.
zh_HANS: 在 UI 侧边栏中显示的插件面板类别.

msgid: Enable custom undo steps for the add-on instead of using the default Blender undo steps.
zh_HANS: 为插件启用自定义撤销步数而不是保持与 Blender 默认撤销步数一致.

msgid: Copy or move a preset to another pack.
zh_HANS: 复制或移动预设到另一个节点包.

msgid: Set the icon for the selected pack.
zh_HANS: 为选定的节点包设置图标.

msgid: Number of days to keep autosave files
zh_HANS: 保留自动保存文件的天数

msgid: Allow overwriting of current edit tree interface if there
zh_HANS: 如果存在则允许覆盖当前编辑树界面

msgid: Redo the last undone action. Hot Node history is isolated from Blender
zh_HANS: 重做上次撤销的操作. 提示: Hot Node 与 Blender 的历史记录是相互独立的.

msgid: Name of the extended menu for adding custom nodes.
zh_HANS: 添加自定义节点的扩展菜单名称.

msgid: The name of the currently selected pack.
zh_HANS: 当前选定节点包的名称.
合并的添加节点菜单标签. 提示: "Add Nodes" 将被自动翻译.

msgid: Delete all presets in the current selected pack.
zh_HANS: 删除当前选定节点包中的所有预设.

msgid: Undo the last action. Hot Node history is isolated from Blender
zh_HANS: 撤销上次操作. 提示: Hot Node 与 Blender 的历史记录是相互独立的.

msgid: Failed to import because the pack name is empty:
zh_HANS: 导入失败, 因为节点包名称为空:

msgid: Filter packs in the add-on panel by the current node tree type in the node editor
zh_HANS: 在插件面板中按节点编辑器中的当前节点树类型过滤节点包

msgid: Name of the default preset for creating nodes preset.
zh_HANS: 创建节点预设的默认预设名称. 提示: "Nodes" 将被自动翻译.
将预设复制到另一个节点包.

msgid: Name of the default pack for creating pack.
zh_HANS: 创建节点包的默认节点包名称. 提示: "NodesPack" 将被自动翻译.

msgid: Show overwrite tree I/O toggle in the side bar.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示覆盖节点树接口选项.

msgid: Show packs in the side bar to select.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示节点包以供选择.
复制 / 拷贝 / 移动预设

msgid: Show duplicate / copy / move preset button in the side bar.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示复制 / 拷贝 / 移动预设按钮.

msgid: Show undo / redo button in the side bar.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示撤销 / 重做按钮.

msgid: Show refresh button in the side bar.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示刷新按钮.

msgid: Show preferences button in the side bar.
zh_HANS: 在插件侧栏显示偏好设置呼出按钮.

msgid: Extend the context menu with a menu containing custom packs for saving nodes.
zh_HANS: 向右键菜单添加一个能够访问所有自定义节点包的菜单以供保存节点.

msgid: Extend the context menu with a list of custom pack menu.
zh_HANS: 向右键菜单添加一列自定义节点包以供保存节点.

msgid: Extend the add nodes menu with a list of custom pack menu.
zh_HANS: 向节点添加菜单添加一列自定义节点包以供添加节点

msgid: Extend the add nodes menu with a menu containing custom packs.
zh_HANS: 向节点添加菜单添加一个能够访问所有自定义节点包的菜单以供添加节点

msgid: Only create new node tree if the node tree interface is different.
zh_HANS: 仅当节点组接口面板不同时才新建节点组

msgid: Always create a new node tree, even if the two trees are the same.
zh_HANS: 总是新建节点组，即使两个节点组的接口面板相同

msgid: Load and update all packs saved with previous versions of Hot Node after add-on got a big update.
zh_HANS: 加载并更新旧版 Hot Node 保存的所有节点包.

msgid: Show the button to load packs from legacy Hot Node version in the UI when there's no pack in the data.
zh_HANS: 当数据中没有节点包时，在 UI 中显示加载旧版 Hot Node 节点包的按钮.
显示加载旧版节点包按钮
加载并更新旧版节点包

msgid: Packs are partially updated, please check the previous reports for details.
zh_HANS: 节点包仅部分加载并更新, 请查看之前的报告以获取详细信息.

msgid: No legacy packs found to update.
zh_HANS: 未找到要加载的旧版节点包.
所有旧版节点包已更新.

msgid: Clean up all data of Hot Node. CANNOT BE UNDONE but you can recover packs from the autosave folder later.
zh_HANS: 清除 Hot Node 的所有数据. 这将无法撤销. 您可以稍后从自动保存文件夹中恢复节点包.

msgid: Show the button to load packs from legacy Hot Node version in the UI when there
zh_HANS: 当数据中没有节点包时，在 UI 中显示加载旧版 Hot Node 节点包的按钮.

msgid: The preset already exists in the pack. Do you want to overwrite it?
zh_HANS: 同名预设已存在于节点包中. 您想要覆盖它吗?

msgid: This operation will clean up all data of Hot Node. CANNOT BE UNDONE but you can recover packs from the autosave folder later.
zh_HANS: 此操作将清除 Hot Node 的所有数据且无法撤销. 您可以稍后从自动保存文件夹中恢复节点包.
热节点插件数据已格式化.

msgid: Hot Node 1.0 have a new structure,
You can still load your old packs
zh_HANS: 您仍可以加载旧节点包

msgid: but may unable to fully done.
you can find it in pack options menu.
zh_HANS: 可在节点包选项中找到.

msgid: Hot Node will try it's best.
Recovered partially successfully, see the previous infos.
zh_HANS: 部分恢复成功, 请查看之前的信息.

msgid: Imported partially successfully, see the previous infos.
zh_HANS: 部分导入成功, 请查看之前的信息.
